  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suika Idle</strong> is a unique incremental game where you easily and simply merge fruits, make juice, and run a café while dreaming of creating the world's best juice!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍉 <strong>Merge Fruits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine two of the same fruit to create a bigger one and earn more money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merge small fruits into larger ones to increase your profits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/d027c2c6979ce7fb174733f24d6cadec.poster.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/d027c2c6979ce7fb174733f24d6cadec.webm?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/d027c2c6979ce7fb174733f24d6cadec.mp4?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🥤 <strong>Make Juice</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Put fruits into a cup to make delicious juice!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can display the juice on the counter and sell it to customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The better the fruit you use, the more expensive the juice will be—so aim to make the best juice possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/5dc0a07dab6e0facc2655af30dd1938f.poster.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/5dc0a07dab6e0facc2655af30dd1938f.webm?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/5dc0a07dab6e0facc2655af30dd1938f.mp4?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📖 <strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience various stories alongside the character, who dreams of making the world's best juice! Watch as they grow and improve through their efforts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/fcdbc01996244bcf51ec2a2978a6936d.poster.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/fcdbc01996244bcf51ec2a2978a6936d.webm?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/fcdbc01996244bcf51ec2a2978a6936d.mp4?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚡ <strong>Upgrade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To expand your café, upgrades are essential!</strong> <br>Increase fruit income, juice prices, and more to boost your profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep upgrading, and the day you create the world's best juice won’t be far away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/a9a0047911907f0a8ba0e0037d0da101.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⭐ Prestige</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to gain special abilities, try <strong>Prestige!</strong> <br>Prestige unlocks powerful new features with stronger effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t miss the chance to grow even further!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/be69485723f3a9d91f1dfc2531cd35fd.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎀 <strong>Decorate Your Café</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your café with stylish decorations!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorations aren’t just for looks—they also provide useful effects to help run your café. Design a fantastic café and boost your business!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/b0b41f34ff0a8c188c62a6d11bae6588.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The challenge to create the world's best juice starts now!</strong> 🚀</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suika Idle</strong> is a unique incremental game where you easily and simply merge fruits, make juice, and run a café while dreaming of creating the world's best juice!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍉 <strong>Merge Fruits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine two of the same fruit to create a bigger one and earn more money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merge small fruits into larger ones to increase your profits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/d027c2c6979ce7fb174733f24d6cadec.poster.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/d027c2c6979ce7fb174733f24d6cadec.webm?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/d027c2c6979ce7fb174733f24d6cadec.mp4?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🥤 <strong>Make Juice</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Put fruits into a cup to make delicious juice!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can display the juice on the counter and sell it to customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The better the fruit you use, the more expensive the juice will be—so aim to make the best juice possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/5dc0a07dab6e0facc2655af30dd1938f.poster.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/5dc0a07dab6e0facc2655af30dd1938f.webm?t=1742792065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https: