c=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/be69485723f3a9d91f1dfc2531cd35fd.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎀 <strong>Decorate Your Café</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your café with stylish decorations!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorations aren’t just for looks—they also provide useful effects to help run your café. Design a fantastic café and boost your business!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436990/extras/b0b41f34ff0a8c188c62a6d11bae6588.avif?t=1742792065\" width=800 height=330 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The challenge to create the world's best juice starts now!</strong> 🚀</p>",
